name: BARFI
description:
Hey,
My name is Babri and I am a stray cat living in a street, north west of  Tehran, A beautiful stranger having an eye on me and each time I visit her balcony she feeds me or leave food behind the door for the time she is not home. She is individual and uses her own saving to buy food and medication for me and many other stray cats around. 
By purchasing my NFT you will help to support me and my pals who also lives in the street.

I love and support stray animals. The sales profit of this collection will be used to support a few individual shelter who does rescue animals. To see the cats story visit @6lovely.cats on Instagram.

Illustrations by @manisaemi
